Old Maid

Victory: getting rid off all your cards
Rules:

The deck will have all the cards but remove 1 of the jokers
The dealer will split all the cards into equal piles.
3 or more players get in a circle.
The player with the joker has the "Old maid"
The goal is to get the player on your left to draw the joker from your deck.
Players drawing cards will take them from the left. 
The dealer will draw first.
Players draw from the person on their left taking 1 card.
If the player gets 2 cards: 
  That match, then the player then gets rid of their match into the center pile and the game continues.
  If the player has the last card that can't be matched then that player has the joker and loses.
